node.name: GraphSummariser-TransformerHybrid
node.description: A hybrid extractive text summarisation system that combines graph-based algorithms (PageRank, HITS) with semantic sentence embeddings from Transformer models like Sentence-BERT. This Python-based tool generates concise, diverse summaries from long documents and is evaluated on benchmark datasets (BBC News, CNN/DailyMail) using ROUGE and BERTScore.
